            <title><![CDATA[Mafia: The Old Country's $50 Price Point Paid Off, Take Two Boss Says]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/mafia-the-old-countrys-50-price-point-paid-off-take-two-boss-says/1100-6536023/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
